question: What are the software developer roles and data analyst roles that are entry level?
sql_query1:
SELECT Roles.title 
FROM Roles
WHERE (Roles.Technology_Career = "Software Developer" OR Roles.Technology_Career = "Data Analyst") AND Roles.Grade = "Entry"
sql_query2:
SELECT Roles.title 
FROM Roles
WHERE Roles.Technology_Career = "Software Developer" OR Roles.Technology_Career = "Data Analyst" AND Roles.Grade = "Entry"
interpretation1: What software developer roles are entry level and what data analyst roles have the same grade?
interpretation2: Provide a list of all software developer roles and also provide a list of all data analyst roles with a entry level grade.
